Package org.locationtech.geowave.adapter.vector.plugin.visibility

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ColumnVisibilityManagementSpi<T>
    Provides a strategy to create visibility handlers for each attribute.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FieldLevelVisibilityHandler<T,CommonIndexValue>
    Define visibility for a specific attribute using the VisibilityManagement.
    JsonDefinitionColumnVisibilityManagement<T>
    Object defining visibility is a json structure where each attribute defines the visibility for a field with the same name (as the attribute).
    VisibilityConfiguration
    Describes which attribute in a feature contains the visibility constraints, interpreted by a ColumnVisibilityManagementSpi
    VisibilityManagementHelper
    At the moment, the expectation is that a single GeoServer instance supports only one visibility management approach/format.
